description.en:
Chibi inu is one of the first movers in coming up with an NFT marketplace for Doge NFTs & memes. The platform also provides charity for dog shelters. Chibi is set to create the best Defi platform in this space. Don’t miss out on the grand Public Sale.

Chibi is primarily made to help dog shelters backed by the NFT marketplace made extensively for memes & dog NFTs. The ownership is renounced with great tokenomics to ensure maximum returns for early backers and investors.
